data.description: Discover the perfect blend of convenience and comfort in this charming single-story home, ideally situated in a peaceful Oceanside community. This centrally located gem offers easy access to the 76 freeway, making your daily commute a breeze.  Step inside to find a welcoming haven with recent upgrades, including a Brand-New Air Conditioning System, Garage Door, plush Carpets, and stylish Ceiling Fans with remote controls. The fully fenced yard ensures PRIVACY and security for your pets, while the spacious driveway provides ample parking space for you and your guests.  With trails, shopping and schools nearby, this home offers the ideal location for anyone seeking the ultimate in convenience. Don't miss out on the chance to make this wonderful property your new home. Act now and come check it out!
